arts.ttl: Girona moves off the bottom of La Liga after holding on to beat Valencia
arts.sum: Diego López equalized in the second half but Girona regained the lead shortly after through Arnau Martínez following a set-piece. But Cameroonian striker Karl Etta Eyong doubled the lead from close range following a corner.
Aaron Ashley has a correct score prediction for all of this weekend's round of ten fixtures in LaLiga, with games taking place across Friday, Saturday and Sunday.
